@@ @@
+ //IN THE BEGINNING//
A pantheon of impossibly powerful ur-deities tear into each other, destroying one another from the inside-out. Their hollowed-out remains, the corpses of gods, fall to the four corners of Asia, burying deep into the ground.
@@ @@
@@ @@
+ //THREE THOUSAND YEARS AGO//
Three unfathomably powerful ancient civilizations wage an apocalyptic war that leaves the landscape of the world forever changed. Before they can destroy each other, they are obliterated by the **BLACKSTAR**, the first true demigod. The existence and histories of the anomalous empires are suppressed by his magic for thousands of years.
@@ @@
@@ @@
+ //OVER THE PAST THREE CENTURIES//
The anomalous has played a crucial, hidden role in humanity's history. Nations leveraged their supernatural resources in the seven Occult Wars, running parallel to the mundane world's conflicts. The Veiled World is vast, but fragile; the only ones keeping it together are the Foundation, the UN Global Occult Coalition, and the PENTAGRAM, desperately trying to maintain the status quo under the House Accords.
@@ @@
@@ @@
+ //NOW//
The Foundation stumbles across the capital city of the ancient Mekhanite Empire. Feeling blindly, they unleash a power humanity has not seen for eras. Robert Bumaro resurrects the Cult of the Broken God. The ball is thrown into motion.
@@ @@
@@ @@
+ //THE CLOCK IS TICKING//
This dead world is spiraling, careening towards an Occult War that threatens to obliterate not just humanity, but all life on the planet. The hands of history cannot be stopped. Pandora's Box cannot be closed. 

But someone has to try.
@@ @@
